name: Feel Beautiful Hand Towel
description:
With a beautiful pink and mustard floral fabric, and a great little ruffle at the bottom, this cute little hand-towel is bound to make you feel good about yourself every time you see it. 

The towel measures 19in. x 15.5in. The towel can be washed in the regular laundry.

Free shipping.

name: Pretty Polka Dots Hand Towel
description:
This cutie has a bright green zig zag stitch and the cutest little ruffle at the bottom. 

The towel measures 18.5 in. x 15 in. it can be washed with the regular laundry.

Free shipping.

name: Dreaming Sweet Hand Towel
description:
This little towel reminds me of a sweet sleep on a cute pillowcase. Each side of the colorful patch has cute double layer ruffles.

The towel measures 18.5in. x 14.5in. It can be washed in the regular laundry.

Free shipping.

name: Free Bird Tote Bag
description:
This adorable tote bag measures 12.5in. x 12.5in. The inside has a polka dot pocket and a pink gingham trim around the top. The handles are 18in. long. The back is plain off-white, and there is a little side strap where you could hook your sunglasses or keys.

This bag can be washed in cold water and air dried, or dried on very low heat.

Free shipping.
